  "riddle": "1. Begin your journey with a rebellious group of English teenagers, exploring their antics in Skins series 2. Uncover how many episodes make up this second chapter.\n\n2. Follow the trace of a famous party-enhancing substance. In the realm of Pharmacology, count the sections that unfold its chemical enchantment.\n\n3. Discover the vibrant culture of underground festivities. How many street dance styles are mentioned in the first breath of this lively gathering's description?\n\n4. Let the numbers dance further—take the figure you just found and consider the sum of its unique prime factors.\n\n5. A grand city by the Thames once held an empire's heart. Seek its 2011 population figure hidden in its urban overview.\n\n6. Ascend in thought to find how far above sea level this city stands.\n\n7. Near this metropolis, count the institutions of higher learning scattered around.\n\n8. Blend the heights and scholarly numbers of the previous two quests.\n\n9. Now, cast your gaze north to a city whose historic streets and ancient crests define a country. Unveil the altitude where its coordinates rest.\n\n10. Delve deeper; consider how many ways you can divide this towering value you just found.\n\n11. Explore ancient tales where democracy was sown, and discover how many tongues convey its story through the pages.\n\n12. At the heart of a kingdom once united, uncover its collective populace as recorded today.\n\n13. Let the past, heights, institutions, and a northern city's altitude guide your final step. Compute the digital root of your discoveries from clues 1, 6, 8, and 9, and unveil the single-digit treasure you seek.",
